    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Bank KB Indonesia Tbk, together with its subsidiaries, provides commercial banking products and services to cooperatives in Indonesia. The company offers saving, demand deposit, time deposit, and current accounts. It also provides consumer, syndicated, joint financing, and channeling loans; financing, and banking services. The company operates through a network of branches, sub-branches, and functional offices, as well as ATMs.It has operations in Jakarta, Bogor, Tangerang, Bekasi, Java, Sumatera, Kalimantan, and internationally. The company was formerly known as PT Bank KB Bukopin Tbk and changed its name to PT Bank KB Indonesia Tbk in August 2025. PT Bank KB Indonesia Tbk was founded in 1970 and is headquartered in Jakarta, Indonesia. PT Bank KB Indonesia Tbk is a subsidiary of KB Kookmin Bank.",
